            "heading": "Frequently Asked Questions",
            "items": [
              {
                "question": "How quickly can you respond to an emergency?",
                "answer": "We aim to be on-site within 60 minutes anywhere in Berlin, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. For standard bookings, we're usually available same-day or next-day."
              },
              {
                "question": "Are your electricians licensed and insured?",
                "answer": "Yes. All ElectroFix electricians are VDE-certified, fully insured, and registered with the Berlin Chamber of Skilled Crafts. We provide certificates for all notifiable work."
              },
              {
                "question": "Is there a callout fee?",
                "answer": "No callout fee on weekday standard bookings. Emergency callouts (evenings, weekends, bank holidays) have a flat €89 first-hour rate, which includes diagnosis."
              },
              {
                "question": "Do you work on commercial properties?",
                "answer": "Yes. We work with offices, retail units, restaurants, and landlords across Berlin. Ask about our planned maintenance contracts for ongoing support."
              },
              {
                "question": "Can you help with EV charger grants?",
                "answer": "Absolutely. We're an approved installer and handle the full grant application process for eligible home EV charger installations."
              }
            ]
          },
